sentences.english: One of the world's most beautiful avenues is the Champs Elysees in Paris.
sentences.chinese: 巴黎的香榭麗舍大街是世界上最美的大街之一。

sentences.english: There were more than 100, 000 people everyday came and went in the Champs-Elysees Avenue.
sentences.chinese: 每天在香榭麗舍大街上往來者不下10萬之衆。

sentences.english: I headed in the direction of the Champs-Elysees.
sentences.chinese: 我向香榭麗舍大街那邊走去。

sentences.english: After all, this is a world famous Champs-Elysees ah.
sentences.chinese: 畢竟這是舉世聞名的香榭麗舍大街啊。
